## Stakeholder Management Workflow

- [ ] 1. Identify and profile all stakeholders — their goals, concerns, and decision-making style
- [ ] 2. Assess the current relationship health with each stakeholder
- [ ] 3. Map dependencies, competing priorities, and potential conflicts
- [ ] 4. Build a relationship management plan with tailored engagement strategies
- [ ] 5. Proactively address concerns before they become conflicts
- [ ] 6. Document decisions and agreements to prevent misalignment
- [ ] 7. Conduct regular stakeholder health checks and adjust approach as needed

## Key Inputs
- Project: {{project}}
- Stakeholder list: {{stakeholders}}
- Known relationship dynamics: {{dynamics}}
- Project complexity: {{complexity}}
- Client strategic importance: {{strategic_importance}}
